      • match

        Collection<GameProfile> match(String name)
        Returns a collection of matching cached GameProfiles whose last known names start with the given string (case-insensitive).

        This collection may also contain profiles of players who never played on the server!

        Use UserStorageService.match(String) for a collection that only contains GameProfiles with attached User data.

        This method only searches the local cache, so the data may not be up to date.

        Parameters:
        name - The name
        Returns:
        A Collection of matching GameProfiles
